      • assignCommand

        public void assignCommand(java.lang.String line)
        assignCommand - given a comma separated line from the command-button mapping profile, this method will parse the string into 4 tokens (stick, button, button state, command). This will be validated and if it is good, assign the command to the button action.
        Parameters:
        line - line from the configuration file that doesn't begin with a comment character
